{"tid":1171213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"讓逃犯條例資訊佔領信箱","createTime":"2019-05-25T14:17:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T10:33:17.000Z","uid":136499,"like":48,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"bf40123db749d458cca5ff1217c25e94a94d7ffd","tid":1171213,"uid":136499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T14:17:22.000Z","msg":"知道好多巴打好落力做街站，好多謝你地!!! 除此以外，我覺得可以做多一步。相信大家都知道身邊有好多人都對逃犯條例理解不足，我認為可以善用大廈信箱，強行令資訊進入普遍大眾嘅視線。呢個方法可能已有巴打提出過，但我覺得好有效。只要每棟大廈有一個熱心巴打，就可以令至少上百户家庭接觸到逃犯條例。<br />\n<br />\n方法<br />\n1. 印有以下有關逃犯條例圖樣等嘅紙，亦可宣傳六月九日遊行<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FTBQosV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFTBQosV.jpg&h=3a15245f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 攝入每一戶信箱<br />\n<br />\n3. 完成<br />\n<br />\n我聽日都會準備印，大家行多一步先可以遍地開花"},{"pid":"4c3bc52d2d530381e161128c8c5733a29bc5e00f","tid":1171213,"uid":136499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T14:18:07.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e638e78398cc85ee811f8c377ee0fcf9eda735a7","tid":1171213,"uid":136499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T14:18:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b5e6a85b15199e9673afaa924891e53563d5502","tid":1171213,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T14:18:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63a29455901f7b48bdb3bac5882a699502fc3490","tid":1171213,"uid":136499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T14:19:10.000Z","msg":"大家加油，可能係最後一次可以出力了"},{"pid":"5f908fda7aa59fe3ad4a54795d3d28f9cab8a496","tid":1171213,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T14:19:23.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正諗住做